<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Hello World 大冒險</title><link>https://huihsiang9292.github.io/</link><description>Recent content on Hello World 大冒險</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-tw</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 15 May 2023 05:00:38 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://huihsiang9292.github.io/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>部署hugo網站 (一)</title><link>https://huihsiang9292.github.io/p/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2hugo%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99-%E4%B8%80/</link><pubDate>Mon, 15 May 2023 05:00:38 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://huihsiang9292.github.io/p/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2hugo%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99-%E4%B8%80/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://huihsiang9292.github.io/p/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2hugo%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99-%E4%B8%80/index.png" alt="Featured image of post 部署hugo網站 (一)" />&lt;h1 id="配置環境">配置環境&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="ubuntu">Ubuntu&lt;/h2>
&lt;pre>&lt;code>sudo apt update &amp;amp;&amp;amp; sudo apt upgrade -y
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>
&lt;h2 id="golang">Golang&lt;/h2>
&lt;pre>&lt;code>sudo apt install golang-go -y
go version
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>
&lt;h2 id="git">Git&lt;/h2>
&lt;pre>&lt;code>sudo apt install git -y
git version
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>
&lt;h2 id="hugo">Hugo&lt;/h2>
&lt;pre>&lt;code>sudo snap install hugo
hugo version
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>
&lt;h1 id="建立-github-儲存庫">建立 Github 儲存庫&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="私有儲存庫">私有儲存庫&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>用來存放所有原始檔案，只有你看得到&lt;br>
&lt;code>Repository name&lt;/code> 可以隨意取&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://huihsiang9292.github.io/p/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2hugo%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99-%E4%B8%80/01.png"
width="925"
height="367"
srcset="https://huihsiang9292.github.io/p/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2hugo%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99-%E4%B8%80/01_huc63367c4826d52cb49f3a26d9bee806b_88971_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://huihsiang9292.github.io/p/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2hugo%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99-%E4%B8%80/01_huc63367c4826d52cb49f3a26d9bee806b_88971_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="252"
data-flex-basis="604px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="公開儲存庫">公開儲存庫&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>用來存放public裡的檔案，所有人都看得到&lt;br>
&lt;code>Repository name&lt;/code> 要填上&lt;code>YourName.github.io&lt;/code>&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://huihsiang9292.github.io/p/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2hugo%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99-%E4%B8%80/02.png"
width="920"
height="365"
srcset="https://huihsiang9292.github.io/p/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2hugo%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99-%E4%B8%80/02_huf20a9bce82d5062ccd912836b7ba3158_92843_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://huihsiang9292.github.io/p/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2hugo%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99-%E4%B8%80/02_huf20a9bce82d5062ccd912836b7ba3158_92843_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="252"
data-flex-basis="604px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="配置hugo-theme-stack主題">配置hugo-theme-stack主題&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>打開 vscode 後，clone 私有儲存庫&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://huihsiang9292.github.io/p/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2hugo%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99-%E4%B8%80/03.png"
width="737"
height="97"
srcset="https://huihsiang9292.github.io/p/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2hugo%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99-%E4%B8%80/03_hu04fd449fa0b7965ebd494e341d09b812_8322_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://huihsiang9292.github.io/p/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2hugo%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99-%E4%B8%80/03_hu04fd449fa0b7965ebd494e341d09b812_8322_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="759"
data-flex-basis="1823px"
>&lt;br>
因為資料夾已經存在，加上 &lt;code>--force&lt;/code> 強制執行&lt;/p>
&lt;pre>&lt;code>hugo new site YourBlog --force
cd www
hugo mod init github.com/YourName/YourName.github.io
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>
&lt;p>在 &lt;code>config.toml&lt;/code> 中寫入:&lt;/p>
&lt;pre>&lt;code>[[module.imports]]
path = &amp;quot;github.com/CaiJimmy/hugo-theme-stack/v3&amp;quot;
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>
&lt;p>在本地預覽通常都會加上 &lt;code>-D&lt;/code> ，這樣才能顯示草稿&lt;/p>
&lt;pre>&lt;code>hugo server -D
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://huihsiang9292.github.io/p/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2hugo%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99-%E4%B8%80/04.png"
width="1293"
height="644"
srcset="https://huihsiang9292.github.io/p/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2hugo%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99-%E4%B8%80/04_hue1e75624e06f8ed494fe487731ed670f_41835_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://huihsiang9292.github.io/p/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2hugo%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99-%E4%B8%80/04_hue1e75624e06f8ed494fe487731ed670f_41835_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="200"
data-flex-basis="481px"
>&lt;br>
目前什麼都沒有，所以我們要加入主題提供的範本&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/CaiJimmy/hugo-theme-stack/archive/refs/heads/master.zip" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>content&lt;/a>&lt;br>
把 exampleSite 下的 &lt;code>content&lt;/code> 資料夾複製到目錄下&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/CaiJimmy/hugo-theme-stack-starter/archive/refs/heads/master.zip" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>config&lt;/a>&lt;br>
把 &lt;code>config&lt;/code> 資料夾複製到目錄下，刪除 &lt;code>config.toml&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://huihsiang9292.github.io/p/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2hugo%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99-%E4%B8%80/05.png"
width="186"
height="270"
srcset="https://huihsiang9292.github.io/p/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2hugo%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99-%E4%B8%80/05_hue69386799335a0767754d5661801151e_9430_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://huihsiang9292.github.io/p/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2hugo%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99-%E4%B8%80/05_hue69386799335a0767754d5661801151e_9430_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="68"
data-flex-basis="165px"
>&lt;br>
從 windows 複製到 wsl2 可能會出現帶有 &lt;code>.Identifier&lt;/code> 的檔案，全部刪掉就行了&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="配置-github-action">配置 Github Action&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="說明">說明&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>每次寫完文章都要手動發佈有點麻煩，配置好 action 後，只需要在寫完文章後 push 到 github，網站就會更新&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>actions/checkout : 官方 action，讓 workflow 可以存取 code&lt;/li>
&lt;li>peaceiris/actions-hugo : 配置 Hugo 環境&lt;/li>
&lt;li>peaceiris/actions-gh-pages : 將某個資料夾下的檔案 push 到特定 branch，也支援 push 到別的 repository&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2 id="建立-action">建立 action&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>建立 action 資料夾，加上 &lt;code>-p&lt;/code> 讓它可以一次建立兩層&lt;/p>
&lt;pre>&lt;code>mkdir -p .github/workflows/
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://huihsiang9292.github.io/p/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2hugo%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99-%E4%B8%80/06.png"
width="197"
height="291"
srcset="https://huihsiang9292.github.io/p/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2hugo%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99-%E4%B8%80/06_hu702575254988312aa0ea6b8a9e62a15c_10035_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://huihsiang9292.github.io/p/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2hugo%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99-%E4%B8%80/06_hu702575254988312aa0ea6b8a9e62a15c_10035_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="67"
data-flex-basis="162px"
>&lt;br>
在 &lt;code>deploy.yml&lt;/code> 中寫入:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt"> 1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 8
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 9
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">10
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">11
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">12
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">13
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">14
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">15
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">16
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">17
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">18
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">19
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">20
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">21
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">22
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">23
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">24
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">25
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">26
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">27
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">28
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">29
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">name: Deploy Hugo site to Pages
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">on:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> push:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> branches:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> - main
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> workflow_dispatch:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">jobs:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> build:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> runs-on: ubuntu-latest
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> steps:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> - uses: actions/checkout@v3
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> - uses: peaceiris/actions-hugo@v2
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> with:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> hugo-version: &amp;#39;latest&amp;#39;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> extended: true
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> - run: hugo --gc --minify
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> - uses: peaceiris/actions-gh-pages@v3
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> with:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> deploy_key: ${{ secrets.ACTIONS_DEPLOY_KEY }}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> external_repository: YourName/YourName.github.io
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> publish_branch: main
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> publish_dir: ./public
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h1 id="deploy-key">Deploy Key&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="生成密鑰">生成密鑰&lt;/h2>
&lt;pre>&lt;code>ssh-keygen -t rsa -b 4096 -C &amp;quot;$(git config YourGithubMail)&amp;quot; -f key -N &amp;quot;&amp;quot;
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://huihsiang9292.github.io/p/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2hugo%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99-%E4%B8%80/07.png"
width="185"
height="305"
srcset="https://huihsiang9292.github.io/p/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2hugo%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99-%E4%B8%80/07_hu2d2fa6bfa99dedcbbeba32cd48fcd7c2_10603_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://huihsiang9292.github.io/p/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2hugo%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99-%E4%B8%80/07_hu2d2fa6bfa99dedcbbeba32cd48fcd7c2_10603_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="60"
data-flex-basis="145px"
>&lt;br>
key 是私鑰，key.pub 是公鑰&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="私鑰">私鑰&lt;/h2>
&lt;pre>&lt;code>cat key
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>
&lt;p>將顯示出來的內容全部複製，包含 &lt;code>-----BEGIN OPENSSH PRIVATE KEY-----&lt;/code> &lt;code>-----END OPENSSH PRIVATE KEY-----&lt;/code>，放在私有儲存庫&lt;br>
名稱 : &lt;code>ACTIONS_DEPLOY_KEY&lt;/code>&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://huihsiang9292.github.io/p/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2hugo%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99-%E4%B8%80/08.png"
width="1278"
height="735"
srcset="https://huihsiang9292.github.io/p/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2hugo%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99-%E4%B8%80/08_hu6b400fbd968420f236d7a713dc397bfc_374102_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://huihsiang9292.github.io/p/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2hugo%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99-%E4%B8%80/08_hu6b400fbd968420f236d7a713dc397bfc_374102_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="173"
data-flex-basis="417px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="公鑰">公鑰&lt;/h2>
&lt;pre>&lt;code>cat key.pub
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>
&lt;p>將顯示出來的內容全部複製，放在公開儲存庫&lt;br>
名稱 : &lt;code>Public key of ACTIONS_DEPLOY_KEY&lt;/code>&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://huihsiang9292.github.io/p/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2hugo%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99-%E4%B8%80/09.png"
width="1262"
height="736"
srcset="https://huihsiang9292.github.io/p/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2hugo%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99-%E4%B8%80/09_hu82c2a50051e7f4fe9adcfa59079488c4_253963_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://huihsiang9292.github.io/p/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2hugo%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99-%E4%B8%80/09_hu82c2a50051e7f4fe9adcfa59079488c4_253963_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="171"
data-flex-basis="411px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="部署到-github-pages">部署到 Github Pages&lt;/h1>
&lt;pre>&lt;code>git config --global user.name YourName
git config --global user.email YourMail@example.com
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>
&lt;p>等一會兒，打開瀏覽器輸入 &lt;code>YourName.github.io&lt;/code> 就可以看到網站啦&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>About</title><link>https://huihsiang9292.github.io/about/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://huihsiang9292.github.io/about/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Archives</title><link>https://huihsiang9292.github.io/archives/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://huihsiang9292.github.io/archives/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Search</title><link>https://huihsiang9292.github.io/search/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://huihsiang9292.github.io/search/</guid><description/></item></channel></rss>